It's proven to be a rather miserable summer for Steven Gerrard, who was England's captain as the Three Lions were dumped out the World Cup group stage.

The Liverpool skipper has also seen his team-mate Luis Suarez depart to Barcelona for £75million and has had to reflect on a 2013/14 campaign where the Reds just missed out on the Premier League title to Manchester City.

